data.description: This charming brick-front home offers a comfortable and inviting living space with three bedrooms and one-and-a-half bathrooms and brand new roof just installed may of 2023. The exterior features a beautiful brick facade. As you approach the home, you are greeted by a convenient carport that provides shelter for your vehicle. This feature adds convenience and ease to your daily routine, especially during inclement weather. The kitchen is well-appointed and offers ample space for meal preparation and storage, this kitchen is both functional and aesthetically pleasing. Overall, this brick-front 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home with a carport offers a combination of classic charm, modern convenience, and ample space. With its well-maintained exterior and inviting interior, this property is sure to impress and provide comfort for years to come. Schedule your showings!!
